
# Database Schema

---

## **users**
Stores registered user info.

| Column        | Data Type      | PK/FK | Description                |
|---------------|----------------|-------|----------------------------|
| id            | INT            | PK    | Primary key                |
| username      | VARCHAR(50)    |       | User’s nickname            |
| first_name    | VARCHAR(50)    |       | User’s first name          |
| last_name     | VARCHAR(50)    |       | User’s last name           |
| email         | VARCHAR(100)   |       | User email                 |
| avatar_url    | VARCHAR(255)   |       | URL to user avatar         |
| password_hash | VARCHAR(255)   |       | Hashed password            |
| created_at    | TIMESTAMP      |       | Account creation timestamp |
| deleted_at    | TIMESTAMP      |       | Soft delete timestamp      |

---

## **session_info**
Tracks user sessions (login/device info).

| Column        | Data Type      | PK/FK | Description               |
|---------------|----------------|-------|---------------------------|
| id            | INT            | PK    | Primary key               |
| user_id       | INT            | FK    | References users(id)      |
| session_start | TIMESTAMP      |       | Session start time        |
| session_end   | TIMESTAMP      |       | Session end time          |
| country       | VARCHAR(50)    |       | Country of user           |
| device_type   | VARCHAR(50)    |       | Device type (mobile/desktop) |
| browser       | VARCHAR(50)    |       | Browser name/version      |
| language      | VARCHAR(10)    |       | User language code        |

---

## **content**
Stores all types of content (movies, shows, etc.)

| Column       | Data Type      | PK/FK | Description                  |
|--------------|----------------|-------|------------------------------|
| id           | INT            | PK    | Primary key                  |
| external_id  | VARCHAR(50)    | FK    | External system ID           |
| type         | VARCHAR(20)    |       | Content type (movie, series) |
| created_at   | TIMESTAMP      |       | Creation timestamp           |

---

## **content_genres**
Many-to-many relationship between content and genres.

| Column      | Data Type      | PK/FK | Description                  |
|-------------|----------------|-------|------------------------------|
| id          | INT            | PK    | Primary key                  |
| content_id  | INT            | FK    | References content(id)       |
| genre_id    | INT            | FK    | References genres(id)        |

---

## **genres**
Stores genre names.

| Column | Data Type   | PK/FK | Description      |
|--------|-------------|-------|------------------|
| id     | INT         | PK    | Primary key      |
| name   | VARCHAR(50) |       | Genre name       |


---

## **watchlists**
Tracks content added to user watchlists.

| Column     | Data Type   | PK/FK | Description                |
|------------|------------|-------|-----------------------------|
| id         | INT        | PK    | Primary key                 |
| content_id | INT        | FK    | References content(id)      |
| user_id    | INT        | FK    | References users(id)        |
| added_at   | TIMESTAMP  |       | When content was added      |

---

## **reviews**
Stores user reviews for content.

| Column       | Data Type  | PK/FK | Description              |
|--------------|-----------|-------|---------------------------|
| id           | INT       | PK    | Primary key               |
| content_id   | INT       | FK    | References content(id)    |
| user_id      | INT       | FK    | References users(id)      |
| review_text  | TEXT      |       | Text of review            |
| created_at   | TIMESTAMP |       | Creation timestamp        |

---

## **content_rating**
Stores user ratings for content.

| Column     | Data Type    | PK/FK | Description                |
|------------|-------------|-------|-----------------------------|
| id         | INT         | PK    | Primary key                 |
| content_id | INT         | FK    | References content(id)      |
| user_id    | INT         | FK    | References users(id)        |
| rating     | DECIMAL(2,1)|       | Rating value given by a user|
| created_at | TIMESTAMP   |       | When rating was created     |

  
---

## **favorite_genres**
Tracks users’ favorite genres with ratings.

| Column   | Data Type    | PK/FK | Description                 |
|----------|-------------|-------|------------------------------|
| id       | INT         | PK    | Primary key                  |
| user_id  | INT         | FK    | References users(id)         |
| genre_id | INT         | FK    | References genres(id)        |
| rating   |DECIMAL(2,1) |       | User’s rating for genre      |
